How to install Jenkins 
(prior to start read prerequisites for Jenkins ) ( java 8 is prerequisite)
1--> browse Jenkins for linux
2--> download the Jenkins installable file
3--> copy the downloading file link address
4--> use that copied address in Linux server ( yum install < copied link address > )
5--> start the service ( service Jenkins start )
6--> check the service is running or not ( # netstat -lntp | grep -i 8080 )
7--> use public IP in browser with port number to start jenkins
